{"tid":2262108,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–天然基因變異造就出對人體更為健康的豌豆","createTime":"2020-10-28T23:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T23:06:03.000Z","uid":38861,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e96af29d0590baa1db11cc9d47c26238e9c51656","tid":2262108,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T23:23:49.000Z","msg":"進食高碳水化合物含量的食物，血糖難免會有所增加。長期血糖過高水平的話，將會增加患上二型糖尿病的風險。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U1CCPah.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU1CCPah.jpg&h=d5ac97cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而血糖飄升的幅度，好取決於食物的物理結構、內含的碳水化合物種類、以及進食後所引起的神經及荷爾蒙反應。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）食物的結構，很大程度由相應的蛋白酶主宰。隨著大自然間基因的變異，對應的蛋白酶功效亦會有所不同。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRdeRoK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRdeRoK.jpg&h=11c0d6d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一道負責控制澱粉結構的基因在天然變異下，造就出了rr豌豆品種，並促使其澱粉結構較原本的RR品種相對較長。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）有科學家將這兩種豌豆進行人體測試（Ref1)，並得出有趣的結果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kJuYyB8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkJuYyB8.png&h=7f1e27d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12名健康人士分別進食50克RR及rr豌豆後，食用<del>同佳</del>rr豌豆人士的血糖及胰島素水平明顯比RR豌豆為低。<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）利用機器往豌豆施壓後，RR豌豆呈糊狀形態，而rr豌豆則<del>拒絕自首</del>分成兩塊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SRR8boQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSRR8boQ.png&h=9732d710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對比RR豌豆，rr豌豆最終化成為Butyrate的百分比較之為高。<br />\n<br />\nButyrate是腸道細菌消化碳水化合物的產物，亦即是說rr豌豆相對上地並沒有效被腸道吸收，而是成為了腸道細菌的食物，間接降低了碳水化合物進入血液循環系統的機會。<br />\n<br />\n依照這邏輯的話，若然我們在其他殼物中以依樣胡蘆的方法修改那基因，大有可能會得到進食後血糖提升速度相對上較慢的殼物，長遠能減低糖尿病增長的風險。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\"><span class=\"blue\">like</span></span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kit2ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=5d170245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kit2ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=1913433c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kit2ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=fb580d12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s43016-020-00159-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs43016-020-00159-8&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kit2ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=6b30d438\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s43016-020-00159-8</a>"},{"pid":"11fe832f3826d2feb9bd261430ac2452107e9e00","tid":2262108,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T23:33:13.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<c